
						(Job Portal Website)
Ventureloop: 
 
VentureLoop is the worldwide leader in job postings focused on venture-backed companies.

Ventureloop is a Job portal company which is long-term associated with VCs (Venture Capitals),VCs are the direct clients to ventureloop and VL invests on VCs so VCs are able to post the jobs with free of charge.

Venture Capital firms have been associated with PCs (Portfolio Companies) and so Portfolio Companies are able to post their jobs in Ventureloop site with their VCs rights.

Non-Client VCs are the companies which are not invested by Ventureloop so they are posting jobs with subscription by paying money through Paypal.NCVCs are associated with NCVCPCs (Non-client VCPCs) and so they are able to post their jobs in Ventureloop site with their NCVC payment.

Non-Client PCs are the companies which are also not invested by ventureloop and any firm so they post jobs with subscription by paying money through Paypal.NCPCs have no investors.

Note:  *Each firm has authentication to post the jobs.

Terminologies:
    VL		-> Ventureloop
    VC		-> Venture Capitals
    PC		-> Portfolio Companies
   NCVC	-> Non-client Venture Capital 
   NCPC	-> Non-client portfolio companies	
  NCVCPC	-> Non-client VC PC

